{"type":"text","timestamp":1775830839494,"sessionID":"ses_2884073faffeGkgZBLhfZx1tsf","part":{"id":"prt_d77c41c19001Z9VdwE5KVYzbFo","messageID":"msg_d77c41207001LgcLtciBy4QpGo","sessionID":"ses_2884073faffeGkgZBLhfZx1tsf","type":"text","text":"Done. The delta-spec.md for AR-011 has been written to `changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md` with 10 requirements and their GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios:\n\n1. **JWTManager PublicKey 访问器** — 新增 `PublicKey()` 方法供 inbound 验证使用\n2. **JWTManager ParseAndValidateToken** — RS256 验证、exp/iat/iss 校验、1 分钟 leeway、错误区分\n3. **AuthMiddleware 中间件** — Bearer token 提取、验证、claims 注入、结构化错误响应\n4. **/v1 路由组注册 AuthMiddleware** — 中间件栈顺序：Logger → Recovery → Auth → ConcurrencyLimit\n5. **/health 端点保持公开** — liveness/readiness probe 无需认证\n6. **outbound JWT 签发保持不变** — proxy.go 的 forwardToSandbox 行为不变\n7. **JWT 配置可扩展** — Config 新增 JWTExpiration、JWTIssuer、JWTLeeway 字段\n8. **JWTManager 支持配置注入** — `NewJWTManager(config *JWTConfig)` 支持自定义参数\n9. **编译与测试门禁** — build/test/race 通过，Test-RT-1/RT-2 覆盖，T/C > 0.4","time":{"start":1775830839492,"end":1775830839492}}}
